命令：vim /etc/security/limits.conf

*           soft  core   unlimit
*           hard  core   unlimit
*           soft  fsize  unlimited
*           hard  fsize  unlimited
*           soft  data   unlimited
*           hard  data   unlimited
*           soft  nproc  65535
*           hard  nproc  63535
*           soft  stack  unlimited
*           hard  stack  unlimited
*           soft  nofile  409600
*           hard  nofile  409600


